reviews.review_text:
Very nice  Another great job on this one, the sounds very good and the set Down back then. Am very lucky to have caught this tour and the Summer tour of 82. Thank you for all the work you put into this site. 
 Energy on this tour was threw the roof with the Stephen and all. We more or less figured it was coming after Greensboro sound check 3 times. Wish someone had that.  this show gets 5 stars because it deserves it.
